All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
GameBoard
Holds the backend game logic for the Snake game, including movement and collision checking.
Main
The main method which runs the Snake game.
SnakeFrame
Provides a container for the SnakePanel, allowing for a GUI for the Snake game.
SnakeNode
Provides a data structure for holding the location of the player character (the snake) at any given time in the Snake game.
SnakePanel
Controls the front-end of the Snake game, including GUI and user controls.
